The CDD fee covers both the Bridge Bay at Bannon Lakes gated 55+ neighborhood inside Bannon Lakes and the Bannon Lakes amenities of pickleball, tennis, playground, resort-style pool, lap lane pool, fitness club, resident's club, dog park and jogging trails!
